Now that we have audited the core event loop, tick, and task lifecycle handlers, we have uncovered the **two exact architectural and logical bugs** that are causing your task-flow stalls and resume failures.

Both of these are incredibly subtle, high-severity bugs hidden inside your async-to-sync state boundary.

